  EffectDiscription_ENG: '[DNA Digivolution] Purple Lv.4 + red Lv.4: Cost 0 Digivolve
    unsuspended with the 2 specified Digimon stacked on top of each other.<Raid>
    <Partition (purple Lv.4 & red Lv.4)> [When Digivolving] If DNA digivolving, you
    may play 1 level 5 or lower Digimon card with the [Free] trait from your trash
    without paying the cost. Then, 1 of your Digimon may gain <Rush> for the turn
    and attack a player.'
